snippet.title: Galactic Catch | Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Great for all ages! Play the latest out-of-this-world fishing game from Baobab Studios, 9x Emmy-winning creators of the fan-favorite, "Invasion!" 

FEATURES:
🌋 Explore strange and wild new worlds
🐟 Catch 60+ types of cosmic fish 
🎣 Customize and power up your rods and reels
🪸 Craft your aquarium with decor and prized fish 
🎶 Escape reality with relaxing melodies 
🐳 Save your friends Mac & Cheez (if you can!)

Have a fin-tastic time as you go fishing across galaxies. Take on the role of a trusted robot on a mission to save your friends Mac & Cheez. Catch wonderous alien fish across strange worlds, craft and power up your fishing gear, go on challenging missions, and customize your aquarium with unique decor and prized fish.
